{"tid":2415121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國法院駁回華為索取滙豐內部文件申請","createTime":"2021-02-20T04:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T05:54:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f46feb54e332b2c1659dd443734b7ab5deaacedf","tid":2415121,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"美國指控孟晚舟向滙豐銀行，隱瞞華為與伊朗的交易，違反美國對伊朗的制裁令，尋求把她由加拿大引渡到美國受審。她的律師上星期入稟，要求英國法院下令，滙豐交出帳簿等內部紀錄，希望證明孟晚舟沒有誤導銀行。倫敦高等法院的法官周五，以沒司法管轄權下達命令為由，駁回華為一方的申請，並要求華為支付八萬英鎊訟費，華為對裁決表示失望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=424662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424662&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=beceac92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D424662&h=d27c0d14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=424662</a>"},{"pid":"25524ba2159f37d6463e88c1509d4075c2b83c5e","tid":2415121,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb35c8cf2a0ee657c4ccc46f0dbdf9cd4fefc45","tid":2415121,"uid":293472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:08:02.000Z","msg":"日出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/